YYoga is a yoga, fitness, and wellness company based in Vancouver, British Columbia. It is the largest corporate-owned yoga company in Canada. Terry McBride and Lara Kozan co-founded the company in 2007. McBride is the YYoga's CEO.
In August 2015, the company operated 13 centres and offered 900+ classes in Vancouver, Richmond, Burnaby, North Vancouver, Whistler and Toronto.
